Readme for Authen::Krb5::Easy

Allows easy aquisition and minor manipulation of ticket granting tickets
from a keytab file.

You will need kerberos 5 libraries and headers to build.

Install as a normal perl module:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

